{"type":"message","id":"49f7adc9","parentId":"6c28a96a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:08:48.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself (agent=main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978). There's no actual user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The session shown is just the cron job agent's own session, not a user conversation.\n\nWait, let me think more carefully. The sessions_list shows the cron job's own session (the session that just ran). There are no other sessions with recent user activity. This cron job was triggered but there's no actual user dialogue.\n\nHowever, I need to be careful - the session itself is the cron job session. Let me check if there are any other sessions. It seems like this is the only session, which means there's no active user conversation.\n\nBut wait - should I consider the cron job's own session as an \"active conversation\"? The task says \"检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）\" and \"如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息）\".\n\nLooking at the session, the last message is from the assistant (me) not from a user. \n\nThe only session here is this cron job's own session, not a separate user conversation. The question is whether the cron job detecting itself counts as an active conversation, but logically there should be another user-initiated session to consider. Since I'm currently in a session that was triggered by a cron job rather than a user, and the instructions ask me to check for user messages, I should proceed with the self-learning task. the time I check. So there are no user conversations happening right now.\n\nWait, but looking at the sessions_list result - the session key shows `agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-...` - this IS the current session. The question is whether this counts as an \"active conversation\". The task says to check if there's an active user dialogue, implying I should look for OTHER sessions with recent user activity.\n\nGiven the context and the nature of this cron job, I think the intent is:\n- Is there a user actively chatting with me? (not this cron job)\n- If yes, skip self-learning\n- If no (only this cron job running), do the self-learning\n\nI should execute the self-learning task now.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The cron job is asking me to check for active sessions. The only session returned is the cron job itself. A session running a cron task is not the same as a user actively chatting. I think I should proceed with the self-learning.\n\nLet me do the web search and save the learning notes.","thinkingSignature":"ebb93ffa27dc198db6749a131213262f78b97083571bf029114078c0f204867a"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有一个cron job自身会话（无用户实际对话），执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n1vljauk0ffj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":882,"output":592,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45455,"cost":{"input":0.0002646,"output":0.0007103999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00229443}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775030907137}}
{"type":"message","id":"6de3e74e","parentId":"49f7adc9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:08:48.076Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n1vljauk0ffj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775030928073}}
{"type":"message","id":"b63260b0","parentId":"6de3e74e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:08:53.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for latest information on:\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\nLet me run searches for these topics.","thinkingSignature":"2615bfe73900079fdda29d33e1802db753816930a7be8e38fd9bced41be4433c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m4pwbo9ohw03_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态 政策\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m4pwbo9ohw03_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026 最新趋势\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m4pwbo9ohw03_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 市场动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1989,"output":192,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46162,"cost":{"input":0.0005966999999999999,"output":0.0002304,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00214653}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775030928076}}
